    "Polyp segmentation is crucial in the segmentation of polyps and removing the polyps if it is cancerous (Rahim et al. 2021).",
    "Robust use of technology in the segmentation and prediction of polyps can solve this issue.",
    "If properly implemented, the accuracy and efficiency of the segmentation of the polyp can be increased.",
    "Deep learning is one such field that can make tedious tasks easy for us.",
    "Image segmentation is a challenging technique in polyp segmentation."
